ServiceModelConfigurationElementCollection<ConfigurationElementType> Class

Definition

Represents an abstract base class for a ConfigurationElementCollection used within the System.ServiceModel.Configuration namespace.

In this Article

public abstract class ServiceModelConfigurationElementCollection<ConfigurationElementType> : System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection where ConfigurationElementType : ConfigurationElementnew()

The type of this configuration element.
